msgid ""
"Unlike other Odoo dashboards, :guilabel:`My Dashboard` is not based on Odoo "
"Spreadsheet, but rather on :doc:`Odoo views <../studio/views>`."
msgstr ""
"他のOdooダッシュボードとは異なり、\\ :guilabel:`マイダッシュボード`\\ はOdoo"
