"configure-request>`."
msgstr ""
"署名申請の有効期限は、\\ :ref:`署名申請の設定 <sign/request-signatures/"
"configure-request>`\\ 時にいつでも変更できます。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/request_signatures.rst:176
msgid ""
