"global-filters/create-types>`\\ を示します: \\ :icon:`fa-calendar`\\ （日付）"
"、\\ :icon:`fa-chain`\\ （リレーション）、\\ :icon:`fa-font`\\ （テキスト）"
"、\\ :icon:`fa-toggle-off`\\ （はい/いいえ）、\\ :icon:`fa-caret-down`\\ （選"
"択）、\\ :icon:`fa-hashtag`\\ （数値）。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:372
msgid ""
"**Change the order** in which the global filters are displayed by clicking "
