#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:203
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Send and receive messages`, select the :guilabel:`To` field "
"and choose :guilabel:`Manage phone number list`. Add up to five valid "
"WhatsApp number as recipients, then enter the confirmation codes sent to "
"those phone numbers in WhatsApp to verify."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`メッセージを送受信`\\ の下で、:guilabel:`移動先`\\ フィールドを選"
"択し、:guilabel:`電話番号リストを管理`\\ を選択します。最大5つの有効な"
"WhatsApp番号を受信者として追加し、それらの電話番号にWhatsAppで送信された確認"
"コードを入力して確認します。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:208
msgid ""
"`WhatsApp Cloud API guide <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/"
"cloud-api/get-started#add-recipient-number>`__"
msgstr ""
"`WhatsApp Cloud APIガイド<https://developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/"
"cloud-api/get-started#add-recipient-number>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:214
msgid "WhatsApp API quickstart"
msgstr "WhatsApp APIクイックスタート"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:216
msgid ""
"Once the Meta accounts and app have been configured, "
"click :guilabel:`Continue` to proceed to the WhatsApp :guilabel:`Quickstart` "
"page. This page provides a starting point for configuring the WhatsApp API "
"by adding a phone number and sending an initial test message."
msgstr ""
"Metaアカウントとアプリが設定されたら、:guilabel:`続行`\\ をクリックして"
